PK<br />\n<br />\n但細個讀書只提愛迪生<br />\n<br />\n佢兩人死後N年<br />\n越黎越多人為Tesla平反<br />\n<br />\n好多天才都係死後先多人識欣賞<br />\n因為佢地嘅思維可能超前一般人幾百年以上<br />\n在世當時根本冇乜人同佢地思想同步到<br />\n就好易被世俗誤會"},{"pid":"826c5eabb98be9ea3d247a187e0d1da522d382e6","tid":391474,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T05:14:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>2006年路蘭套死亡魔法已有講Tesla<br />\n仲要主題講魔術好好睇</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/22/033057_47c9084385abc8e62b82e66bf181604a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F22%2F033057_47c9084385abc8e62b82e66bf181604a.jpg&h=33f29f37&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n狼人走去搵佢幫拖 果陣係咁俾愛迪人派人搞9佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77edf18d8c4f5bd5a57f79cb6ac540c0cc902c81","tid":391474,"uid":116896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T05:59:29.000Z","msg":"愛迪生正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b547d6014aa5669811de82399239cf7ffd11217","tid":391474,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:36:46.000Z","msg":"下     愛迪生做正派主角<br />\nTesla 做反派奸角 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  (個 trailer 俾我既感覺)"},{"pid":"ea15f746486f8885c91a3e3639040b72e91f4e0b","tid":391474,"uid":130597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T09:22:15.000Z","msg":"好似見到有蜘蛛仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}